ihu.com/api/v4/people/959df776b9ad5d55043cf942a0424832","user_type":"people","headline":"也许我们明天就相遇，也许只能在两个宇宙里平行~","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561767883","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545998209,"updated_time":1545998209,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":5,"content":"\u003cp\u003e哥德巴赫被证明了，题主立功了！他继承了民科的光荣的传统。高斯、伽罗华、欧拉、拉格朗日在这一刻灵魂附体！题主代表了民科悠久的历史和传统，在这一刻他不是一个人在战斗，他不是一个人！\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560653360,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"2cac466b677ae354356a5306b729ef36","url_token":"synn","name":"宋小狮","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/25c0cdc0c9642e99ae253a3ce544a2a9_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/25c0cdc0c9642e99ae253a3ce544a2a9_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/2cac466b677ae354356a5306b729ef36","user_type":"people","headline":"我不接受你的建议。","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560653360","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545877069,"updated_time":1545944995,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":2,"content":"\u003cp\u003e每年参加高考的人数是千万人左右，考入清北的人数大约是两三百人，也就是说比例大约是几万分之一，虽然很困难，但并不是完全没有可能。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e可你想证明的哥猜已经提出将近三百年了，三百年里有多少人想要证明而不得？你想过这个比例吗？你觉得证明哥猜比考清北更容易吗？你把三百年里诞生又死去的无数有聪明才智的人放在哪里呢？\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":563532939,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"eb88ff404ab7d5abfb8e3d181575fce4","url_token":"bu-ru-zuo-ti-qu-73","name":"不如做题去","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-2549c070b4877b2d878ac09a66451f44_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-2549c070b4877b2d878ac09a66451f44_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/eb88ff404ab7d5abfb8e3d181575fce4","user_type":"people","headline":"学生","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563532939","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546247459,"updated_time":1546247459,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":2,"content":"\u003cp\u003e首先，身为一个高中生肯去了解甚至是钻研哥德巴赫猜想。绝大多数都是对于这个问题的好奇，和对数学的热爱。而不是为了被清华北大录取而潜心研究的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e无论怎么样，证明哥德巴赫猜想也好，还是做别的事情也罢，都希望你是为了自己的兴趣，自己的喜好而去努力。而不是带着目的性，比如什么被清华北大录取的想法之类的去做一件事情。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e不善言辞，但是希望你能明白！\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560688701,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"c8682073c52303e98680b6e26de1fa75","url_token":"ji-wu-li-3","name":"田百顷","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-51108b0521954376194817154391e49b_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-51108b0521954376194817154391e49b_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/c8682073c52303e98680b6e26de1fa75","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560688701","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545879564,"updated_time":1545928323,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":64,"content":"\u003cp\u003e一群XX博士XX博士后，跟一个中学生这么较真，上来不管三七二十一，就先嘲讽一顿再说。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e你们嘲讽得那么痛快，为的是什么？就为了证明你比一个中学生的岁数更大，见识更多？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e一个三岁小孩，声音大，吵到你了，你是不是也要跟他对吵，还讥讽：就你这嗓门，一辈子不用开口了？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e一个三岁小孩，好动，碰到你了，你是不是也要跟他对打，还讥讽：就你这力气，一辈子不用动手了？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e中学本来就是人人都在中二，满脑子异想天开的时候，谁不是这么过来的？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e即便自古文人相轻，相互看不起，也用不着跟一个还没起步的中学生较真吧？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e—————————————————————————————————————\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e讲个故事吧：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我大学的时候跟一个家在农村的老乡一起去餐馆吃饭，点菜的时候，那人想点一份干锅茶树菇，我当时不乐意，因为这玩意吃的太多了，于是就不停地说，别点这玩意了，吃了不知道多少次了。然后对方默默地说了句，我没吃过嘛，这时我才注意到，对方脸色已经很不好了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e怎么样，是不是觉得我当时很贱？我现在也是这么觉得的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e同理，很多你觉得显而易见理所当然的常识性的东西，不是所有人都知道。所以，不要你比别人多懂一些东西，就一副高高在上的姿态，把别人评价一遍，数落一遍。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e—————————————————————————————————————\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e见到一种论调：我讥讽你，嘲笑你，都是在为你好。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e…………\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这是在玩sm啊？我鞭笞你，辱骂你，践踏你，不是因为我有什么奇怪的嗜好，而是为了让你享受。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e所以，就是一些人在过过嘴瘾而已，不要说得那么高尚。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e—————————————————————————————————————\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e又见一类论调：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e你是高中生了，应该为自己的行为负责。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e你在网上发言，要为自己言论负责。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e你功利心强，侮辱了数学，活该被骂。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e…………\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e嗯，总而言之，我就是要骂你。（到这一步，就是正儿八经的网络暴力了）\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e—————————————————————————————————————\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e刚刚评论区又一个：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e其他人没嘲笑他啊，都是在热情地提供帮助。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e…………\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e呵呵，这些所谓正经回答，热心帮助的，有几个真心觉得一个高中生能解决哥德巴赫猜想？明知道不可能，还假惺惺地提供帮助，不就是在起哄，凑热闹，消遣人？这不叫嘲讽，什么叫？就好比，一个恶霸说，你来打我呀，是真让你去打他吗？就是吃定了你不敢打，才这么说来耍你玩的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这些人还揣着明白装糊涂，假惺惺地说我们没恶意啊。一旦你将他戳破，他马上又说，这人自作自受，活该被骂。（同上，又成了赤裸裸的网络暴力了）\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e—————————————————————————————————————\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e还有人，说我这么圣母，怎么不去帮助他。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我在路边看到乞丐，一般不会给钱，更不会给他工作帮他安顿下来，但我绝不会嫌他脏就去踹他两脚。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":563710349,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"a476ebbdee2ed3800e9262893cfa1492","url_token":"","name":"知乎用户","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":true},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563710349","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546267871,"updated_time":1546267871,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":2,"content":"\u003cp\u003e说一下追求真理和追求利益，这不是必然矛盾的。物质利益等等功利目的确实不应该是科研的出发点，但是作为目的之一是天经地义无可厚非的，具体权重因人而异，切不可以己度人，也不要轻易猜测别人怎么想。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e热爱和痴迷于数学未必与追求金钱名利矛盾，追求金钱名利也未必就不会做出科研成就，因为你不能武断的认定追求名利在别人的心理有多大权重。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e不要一句话就否定了一个天才同时追求学术和追求名利的权利，这样的人未必存在，但你不能就断定他不存在。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e最后举一个例子，牛顿，又炒股又当造币厂厂长又和别人争论发明权，你说牛顿视名利如粪土我是不信的，但是谁能否定他的伟业？也没没有谁会去否定牛顿对科学的纯粹的热爱吧？又何必去否定一个既热爱科学又对名利有所追求的人呢？焉知别人不是下一个牛顿？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e当然肯定不会是这位在知乎上吹牛逼的高中生哈哈 \u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":563716574,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"95397d7451dde93644b3b28cfa2809bf","url_token":"li-xiao-gang-75-96","name":"argv","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-793ce6cb7dabebaaf98d672a9a8bdbdd_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-793ce6cb7dabebaaf98d672a9a8bdbdd_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/95397d7451dde93644b3b28cfa2809bf","user_type":"people","headline":"Only living so long, I just skip that proof.","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563716574","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-996514fc76d52d943b93a5f91c62091b_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546268491,"updated_time":1546310445,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":2,"content":"\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-89594c46646404ac19119422e9d204d4_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"1734\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-6fdbf8991b6091605e7f5bc858b7fe7b_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-89594c46646404ac19119422e9d204d4_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1080'%20height='1734'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"1734\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-6fdbf8991b6091605e7f5bc858b7fe7b_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-89594c46646404ac19119422e9d204d4_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-89594c46646404ac19119422e9d204d4_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e哎，不是。我就想问问，现在的高中生都怎么了？动不动就哥猜，解释世界。你们是不是以为，前人的脑子是长脑袋的时候附赠的。他们穷尽一生都没完成的事儿，你们哪来的自信，没接受完初等教育就能完成。。。。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e另外，你们说的清华北大，和我了解的清华北大是一个东西吗？清华北大保送条